    <p>
        Since the beginning of the New Year, and the new lockdown precautions within the UK, there have been several new Covid-19 schemes aimed at small businesses and those who are Self-Employed. With the third lockdown looking to be extended into March, and even potentially into the Summer, we have compiled a short list of new schemes which have been introduced in the interest of helping those in need.
